commitResults.messageTitle: Refactor: Update data model and input requirements
commitResults.messageBody:
This commit replaces individual person context with company context to align with broader organizational scope. Additionally, it modifies the data requirements:
- Changed compulsory phone number field to compulsory tag field.
- Updated phone number field to be optional, reflecting evolving user needs.

These changes enhance flexibility and accommodate diverse usage scenarios while maintaining data integrity.
